snippet: Crippling cargo backups at U.S. West Coast ports dragged on into a third month amid industry reports on Thursday of prolonged shipment delays for goods ranging from yoga apparel and rice to NBA bobblehead collectibles and frozen french fries....

headline.print_headline: U.S. West Coast Port Backups Delay Apparel, Bobbleheads, French Fries
headline.main: U.S. West Coast Port Backups Delay Apparel, Bobbleheads, French Fries

lead_paragraph: Crippling cargo backups at U.S. West Coast ports dragged on into a third month amid industry reports on Thursday of prolonged shipment delays for goods ranging from yoga apparel and rice to NBA bobblehead collectibles and frozen french fries.
